15. Solitude - Duke Ellington/Coleman Hawkins
16. Girl From Ipanema, The - Archie Shepp



The archives of Bob Thiele's Impulse label offer this collection of reinterpreted jazz standards, including Art Blakey's "Summertime," Duke Ellington and John Coltrane's "In a Sentimental Mood," Benny Carter's "Body and Soul" and Charles Mingus's "Mood Indigo," as well as material from Shelly Manne, Archie Shepp and Count Basie.
